      "id": "PopularPost114848",
      "post_content": "If you want to pump up all your creatures for one all-out attack, they're likely little goblins who will die in the slide anyway. If you want to wipe your opponent's swarm of creatures, well, you're playing red - you have [Pyroclasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm) and [Rolling Thunder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rolling Thunder).  \n  \nIt's pretty neat... but it's certainly hard to use, at the very least.",
